snippet.title: Exist.EXE Trailer
snippet.description:
Exist.EXE is a puzzle game that follows the self-discovery journey of a game developer who is trapped in a distorted game world.
Marcus will travel across a world constructed with various biome data and work with his assistant to solve puzzles by hacking and spawning objects.

Demo download link : https://skyfeathergame.itch.io/existexe
